msgid ""
"Teams optimize for different goals, such as startup latency, sustained "
"throughput, memory footprint, elasticity, and cost.\n"
"Quarkus addresses these needs by shifting work from run time to build time, "
"keeping one development model across JVM and native, and exposing production "
"signals such as health checks, metrics, and tracing."
msgstr ""
"团队针对不同的目标进行优化，例如启动延迟、持续吞吐量、内存占用、弹性和成本。Quarkus通过将工作从运行时转移到构建时、在JVM和本地开发中保持统一的开发模型以及公开生产信号（如健康检查、指标和跟踪）来满足这些需求。"

#: _posts/2025-11-27-mmaler-blogpost-2-quarkus-runtime-and-framework-for-cloud-native-java.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Start with **JVM mode** for most services.\n"
"On the JVM, Quarkus often starts faster and uses less memory than "
"traditional JVM-based runtimes because it performs more work at build time.\n"
"Just-in-time compilation raises steady-state throughput, scales well across "
"cores, and offers mature garbage collectors and tuning options.\n"
"The JVM also provides rich observability and diagnostics, which help you "
"understand and tune live systems."
msgstr ""
"大多数服务使用 *JVM 模式* 启动。在 JVM 上，Quarkus 的启动速度通常比传统的基于 JVM "
"的运行时更快，内存使用量也更少，因为它在构建时执行了更多工作。即时编译提高了稳态吞吐量，在不同内核间扩展良好，并提供成熟的垃圾回收器和调整选项。JVM "
"还提供丰富的可观察性和诊断功能，帮助您了解和调整实时系统。"

#: _posts/2025-11-27-mmaler-blogpost-2-quarkus-runtime-and-framework-for-cloud-native-java.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Use **native mode** when startup latency and memory footprint are strict "
"constraints.\n"
"Native executables start in milliseconds and can use less memory, which "
"supports scale-to-zero workflows and lowers idle costs on small instances.\n"
"Trade-offs include lower peak throughput, limited multi-core scaling, a "
"single-threaded garbage collector in current native images, longer build "
"times, and a slower inner loop for developers."
msgstr ""
"当启动延迟和内存占用有严格限制时，请使用 *本地模式* "
"。本机可执行文件在几毫秒内启动，使用的内存更少，从而支持从零扩展到零的工作流，并降低小型实例的闲置成本。折衷方法包括降低峰值吞吐量、限制多核扩展、在当前的本地映像中使用单线程垃圾回收器、延长构建时间以及降低开发人员的内循环速度。"

#: _posts/2025-11-27-mmaler-blogpost-2-quarkus-runtime-and-framework-for-cloud-native-java.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If your system needs both profiles, split by workload.\n"
"Run bursty or event-driven endpoints in native mode, and run long-lived high-"
"throughput services on the JVM."
msgstr "如果您的系统需要两种配置文件，请按工作负载进行划分。在本地模式下运行突发或事件驱动端点，在 JVM 上运行长期高吞吐量服务。"

#: _posts/2025-11-27-mmaler-blogpost-2-quarkus-runtime-and-framework-for-cloud-native-java.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Observability note.**\n"
"JVM mode exposes richer diagnostics and metrics, including GC, heap, and "
"thread telemetry, JFR, and profiler support, which makes issue triage and "
"performance tuning easier.\n"
"Native mode still exports application-level metrics and traces with "
"Micrometer and OpenTelemetry, but it offers fewer VM-level signals."
msgstr ""
"*可观察性说明。* JVM 模式可提供更丰富的诊断和指标，包括 GC、堆、线程遥测、JFR "
"和剖析器支持，从而使问题分流和性能调整变得更容易。本地模式仍可通过 Micrometer 和 OpenTelemetry "
"输出应用级指标和跟踪，但提供的虚拟机级信号较少。"

